            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "陳法拉被勒令減肥靠「嗱喳招」過關 爆張家輝連鉸剪擺位都緊張過人丨專訪",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"陳法拉被勒令減肥靠「嗱喳招」過關 爆張家輝連較剪擺位都緊張過人。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/cf733db864a6867286ab1ea1fdef3e17/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041521342164902.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">陳法拉被勒令減肥靠「嗱喳招」過關 爆張家輝連較剪擺位都緊張過人。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>陳法拉在張家輝自導自演的《贖夢》中飾演張家輝老婆，二人因一次投資嚴重失利，陷入一個萬劫不復的巨變，法拉更因此變得瘋癲。作為「緊張大師」的家輝不樣樣都執到正，連把鉸剪放在哪個位置都計得好準，更認為法拉片中角色長期處於陰暗狀態，勒令她要減肥演出。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉為拍《贖夢》港美兩邊走。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb9158e1151318f1aa190c390e068144/2025-04/IMG_7670.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉為拍《贖夢》港美兩邊走。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉笑談拍《贖夢》點滴。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9e84b1f83a8ceca79e9ccc7238dbe4ab/2025-04/IMG_7671.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉笑談拍《贖夢》點滴。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉有瘦面絕招。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/391dbd67124cac67f32c61a3c1c9b03f/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_01_07_39.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉有瘦面絕招。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法拉拍新片好難忘。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f3fd0924ac5ae7c7ce93377613ac50f0/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_01_07_41_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法拉拍新片好難忘。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"拍《贖夢》有回家感覺。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/000a5789396e9a9148d9d69ba0c59ebc/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_01_07_41_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        拍《贖夢》有回家感覺。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法拉拍《贖夢》好有滿足感。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8b22c236e7f589442fbed628cd1a347d/2025-04/IMG_7672.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法拉拍《贖夢》好有滿足感。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>為了參與這部電影，法拉兩個多月來香港美國兩邊走，早前更特意回港3日2夜為電影落力宣傳。她直言接拍這部電影是因為恩人鍾珍小姐，「監製鍾珍是我的恩人，她一開聲，我便二話不說回來了！」法拉又爆導演家輝要求她減肥，估計主要是因為她飾演一個失利後，長期處於瘋癲狀態而變得失魂落魄，可惜當時正值撞正聖誕節，她和家人去了法國，美食當前相當大誘惑，法拉自爆拍硬照時唯有出「嗱喳招」瘦臉，並笑言：「家輝自稱減咗好多磅，我就減咗10磅，但我望落去唔覺，特別上鏡都未覺好瘦，影硬照時我就出『嗱喳招』，咬住個腮，望落去就會瘦啲，但拍攝時講對白就冇辦法啦。」她又指監製鍾珍是魔鬼之一，一邊叫他們減肥，一邊不停買外賣宵夜，更有龍躉：「佢（鍾珍）話係冇油嘅白灼龍躉，但係好大兜，好開心嘅，日日開工都有好嘢食。」\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"片中陳法拉及張家輝兩公婆投資嚴重失利。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/13d0b7246fb1dc7fe592f4287b5bfeb8/2025-04/2e1f0511-9d1f-42dd-8682-fe65914afabf.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        片中陳法拉及張家輝兩公婆投資嚴重失利。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法拉長期處於瘋癲狀態而變得失魂落魄。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d1a5d0972f8f3a76d08a6ee2f1cd55e/2025-04/174472295314412.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法拉長期處於瘋癲狀態而變得失魂落魄。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"正值聖誔節同老公Emmanuel Straschnov米蘭度假。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ed9af3eb80174c8257ba3ef7403757e/2025-04/174472295349424.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        正值聖誔節同老公Emmanuel Straschnov米蘭度假。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"卻接獲減肥任務。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0ec7017f520ef5476e234f235bab18e3/2025-04/10_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        卻接獲減肥任務。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法拉再婚後建立幸福家庭。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9ccb304d1803eeec1cd0d6aedfa5930c/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2021-11-22_at_13_42_14_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法拉再婚後建立幸福家庭。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>大讚家輝好精準</strong>\n</p>\n<p>談到首次參與家輝執導的電影可有壓力？法拉笑言：「我諗我畀壓力佢多啲，因為第一次合作。家輝好清楚自己劇本、想點拍點演，所以我就畀佢帶住去做。因為我哋冇合作過，佢都要好信任我。」她又大讚家輝好精準，連把鉸剪放在哪個位置都計得好準，令她不用想太多，放心專注演戲，是一個很特別的體驗。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"戲外陳法拉及張家輝手拖手赤腳跑街鬆弛一下。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76a3bcc4714a65596888a93a4a5ec020/2025-04/DSC02101.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        戲外陳法拉及張家輝手拖手赤腳跑街鬆弛一下。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉最難忘跳樓一幕場口。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/097464672e5793fb227d48cad08ddd8f/2025-04/174472368250209.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉最難忘跳樓一幕場口。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"家輝會親自在場度好每個鏡位。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/86e68ad4fa4fbf5708d1a015033ff69f/2025-04/c027d69f-4761-4baf-a094-5f40dbd2fe28.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        家輝會親自在場度好每個鏡位。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法拉大讚家輝好精準。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6312ade387a0deaffee94a53bd8373e7/2025-04/01_25.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法拉大讚家輝好精準。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉反而畀壓力張家輝。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f6eb8ee9c468fdb8c806dcb86a2be227/2025-04/03_14.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉反而畀壓力張家輝。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉、張家輝合作有火花。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa6a314e02d06dc0a8e0874e5d1c3ca2/2025-04/IMG_8184.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉、張家輝合作有火花。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>法拉曾自導自演的短片《人來人往》，今次會否特別明白家輝的要求或更有默契？法拉指自己的相對簡單，反而家輝這部電影製作較大，而且已經籌備多年，加上他要兼顧多個職位，同時又要投入相對沉重的角色，當中有些故事更是家輝真真正正自己的夢境，法拉大讚對方好叻，十分有毅力，坦言非常佩服。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"法拉曾自導自演的短片《人來人往》。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2c744cc3b4d0d0c658444981e538413f/2025-04/174472339766119.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        法拉曾自導自演的短片《人來人往》。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"陳法拉對做導演有心得。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/600e7e3056e6599991cc0f954b11f680/2025-04/thumbnail_1_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳法拉對做導演有心得。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>恨同劉俊謙過招</strong>\n</p>\n<p>法拉2016年曾與劉俊謙合作舞台劇《前度》，相隔近9年再度合作，可惜今次只得一場對手戲，法拉坦言感到失望，並大讚對方當年做舞台劇，只是剛剛畢業，現在可以獨當一面做男主角，非常厲害，並希望將來有更多機會可以跟對方「過招」。最後，法拉表示每一部戲都是一種緣份，今次能夠與家輝及認識了多年的鍾珍合作，非常高興，至於，什麼時候會再來港拍戲？她就表示要很多考慮因素，還是一切隨緣。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子華、陳法拉及劉俊謙演過舞台劇劇《前度》，今次再跟劉俊謙合作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/aa07fe1e37e3c0ebe43ea0e2557aab49/2025-04/174472343261975.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子華、陳法拉及劉俊謙演過舞台劇劇《前度》，今次再跟劉俊謙合作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><pre>\nCredit ：\n化妝：Mon Cheng\n髮型：Alex So @ The Attic\n服裝：Tory Burch\n鞋：Christian Louboutin\n高級珠寶：CHANEL\n場地：制作基地有限公司</pre>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064148/即時-娛樂-陳法拉被勒令減肥靠-嗱喳招-過關-爆張家輝連鉸剪擺位都緊張過人丨專訪",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-16 07:11:07",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "搶先雷軍一步？黃子韜出衛生巾1分鐘賣出近5萬單 二手平台被炒賣",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"黃子韜推出衛生巾，1分鐘賣出近5萬單，¥0.01衛生巾二手平台最高被炒至500元。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/5394c39c30d70a71a5e3cc75e7761b3b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250415/_2025041516202353313.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">黃子韜推出衛生巾，1分鐘賣出近5萬單，¥0.01衛生巾二手平台最高被炒至500元。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>內地衛生巾接連爆出醜聞，嚴重打擊消費者信心，早前已有網民要求小米雷軍推出衛生巾。不過，小米還沒有消息時，內地歌手黃子韜近日已在直播間開售他合夥收購的衛生巾工廠做的產品，以1分錢的價格賣出49500份給顧客試用。在直播間中，黃子韜和工作人員稱，其產品屬於「醫護級」，並通過了多項檢測。\n\n</p><h2>4天漲粉超11萬</h2>\n<p>數據顯示，黃子韜衛生巾品牌賬號「朵薇官方旗艦店」4月11日粉絲總量為1.1萬，目前為12.9萬，4天漲粉超11萬。同日，黃子韜在直播間首次展示了他合夥收購的衛生巾工廠做的產品——「朵薇蠶絲醫護級衛生巾禮盒」，以1分錢每單的價格，上架了近5萬單衛生巾給顧客試用，衛生巾在1分鐘內被搶購一空。\n\n</p>\n<p>黃子韜在直播介紹自己工廠製作的衛生巾，展示衛生巾檢測報告。黃子韜介紹，這是醫護級衛生巾，「全程透明化製作，未來還會有App上線，用戶可以實時監督。無人工接觸。第一個碰到這個衛生巾的人，就是每一個用戶。」據悉，工廠生產的衛生巾預計在5月中下旬線上發售。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3438625/\">小米刪不造衛生巾微博成熱搜 網民：許願成功？</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間首次展示了他合夥收購的衛生巾工廠做的產品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/530a4726121473a239ec3e4f579eb636/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-15-15h27m07s567.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間首次展示了他合夥收購的衛生巾工廠做的產品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間首次展示了他合夥收購的衛生巾工廠做的產品。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a4ae2b810cda832c48a2d8e9db0ad1fc/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-15-15h27m25s541.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間首次展示了他合夥收購的衛生巾工廠做的產品。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/51f9aba5ed8bf77ffac78c2bd0a1400a/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-15-15h27m34s008.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c78b5ea23be0763e9043eab193051091/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-15-15h27m47s648.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/675886262439f9b9ef1572d04b3f8fd5/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-15-15h27m55s694.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/902d7f7c4fd03c1e9648a15177ba50b9/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-15-15h28m13s402.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>衛生巾二手平台被炒高價</h2>\n<p>根據其直播間掛售的衛生巾鏈接顯示，當前衛生巾禮盒的定價為49.9元（人民幣，下同）22片，每片平均價2.27元，涵蓋了日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。據了解，目前內地市面上的日用衛生巾單片價格在1元左右，安睡褲的價格則在每片3元左右。\n\n</p>\n<p>與此同時，部分湧入直播間的「黃牛」，也在二手交易平台上線搶購來的衛生巾，價格有19元、49元、69元、200元、500元不等。甚至還有用戶組織相關拍賣活動，有一拍賣帖子顯示，起拍價4元，瀏覽量高達2824次，25人點「想要該物品」。對此，黃子韜在直播間發聲抵制網上炒的轉賣行為。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3437933/\">央視3.15｜曝光翻新衛生巾、嬰兒紙尿片 多個品牌次貨被「加工」售賣</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc97dbc85de67a8ab1d66b100ab10d81/2025-04/_MG_4744.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/fc78bccbd0538a5e128a2d1318e693cb/2025-04/Clipboard41_5.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜在直播間展示自家生產衛生巾日用款、迷你巾以及安睡褲。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜衛生巾品牌賬號「朵薇官方旗艦店」4天漲粉超11萬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9d7e44823caba01dd7ff29de4b0d4f8f/2025-04/Clipboard42_5.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜衛生巾品牌賬號「朵薇官方旗艦店」4天漲粉超11萬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"企查查APP資料。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a2035b7acf2bca510c689d1f23d8cbd1/2025-04/Clipboard43_5.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        企查查APP資料。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"企查查APP資料。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c3bad21f6642aff3d4baff6836727286/2025-04/Clipboard44_5.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        企查查APP資料。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"朵薇蠶絲醫護級衛生巾禮盒以¥0.01賣近5萬單。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/58e7d67efa4dd956660f39f0e2edb674/2025-04/Clipboard45_4.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        朵薇蠶絲醫護級衛生巾禮盒以¥0.01賣近5萬單。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"二手平台出現競拍及炒賣。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b233adc340f7fc7633c565f7de85c14c/2025-04/Clipboard46_4.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        二手平台出現競拍及炒賣。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜介紹未來還會有App上線，用戶可以實時監督。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/08cc08a260b2411b53ea5889a409f7e5/2025-04/Clipboard47_2.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜介紹未來還會有App上線，用戶可以實時監督。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜稱旗下工廠產的屬醫護級衛生巾。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/43af3620e2716ced1f56678575926cff/2025-04/Clipboard48_4.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜稱旗下工廠產的屬醫護級衛生巾。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"黃子韜。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/92dfe3bdfdb42ed7fb00e90733c675ac/2025-04/IMG_1672.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        黃子韜。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>收購衛生巾工廠 全新設備生產</h2>\n<p>有網友質疑，黃子韜生產的衛生巾為何取名為「朵薇」，是否為「代工廠生產」？黃子韜在直播中回應表示，自己收購了一個衛生巾工廠，該工廠過去的生產工序已全部停掉，新工廠是全新的設備。之所以收購衛生巾工廠是為了增強自己的責任感，且將工廠生產全過程透明化展現在用戶面前。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3402567/\">公關災難︱衛生巾「唔夠長」客服寸回「可以不買」 ABC急道歉下架全部產品</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>企查查APP顯示，該賬號當前認證主體公司即杭州聆玥科技有限公司，成立於2024年6月，近日由浙江朵薇護理用品有限公司接手聆玥科技100%股權，而浙江朵薇公司則由黃子韜名下杭州龍悅謙網絡科技有限公司間接持股。\n\n</p>\n<p>有業內人士表示，黃子韜入局衛生巾行業的優勢在於，其自帶廣告流量效應和粉絲信任基礎。但長期來看，明星網紅跨界入局衛生巾生產行業，還需在行業標準、生產規範、監督管理、用戶真實需求等方面多下功夫。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064090/即時-中國-搶先雷軍一步-黃子韜出衛生巾1分鐘賣出近5萬單-二手平台被炒賣",
